<!-- What Makes 2-in-1 Different -->
<section class="sec bg-white relative py-16">
 <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
 <h2 class="section-title text-center">What Makes 2-in-1 Hybrid Chargers Different?</h2>
 <p class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">A 2-in-1 hybrid charger fuses a foldable AC wall charger with a portable battery. GaN semiconductors shrink the AC circuitry; a built-in or retractable cable eliminates the loose accessory. The result is one travel-sized device that replaces a wall charger, a cable, and a power bank.</p>

 <blockquote class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 bg-brandOrange/5 border-l-4 border-brandOrange rounded-r-xl px-6 py-5 text-sm text-slate-700 italic leading-relaxed">
  <p>"The GaN charger market is projected to grow at a 16.5% CAGR through 2034, from $1.2B to $5.4B. Within this, portable chargers represent ~30% of demand — and the 2-in-1 hybrid segment is the fastest-growing subcategory, driven by post-pandemic travel and USB-C device consolidation. One device that charges from the wall and doubles as a power bank is no longer a novelty; it's becoming the consumer expectation."</p>
  <cite class="block text-xs text-slate-400 mt-2 not-italic">— <a href="https://exactitudeconsultancy.com/reports/48745/gan-powered-chargers-market" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brandOrange hover:underline">Exactitude Consultancy</a>, GaN Powered Chargers Market Report 2025-2034</cite>
 </blockquote>

 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 text-center">
 <p class="text-3xl font-black text-brandBlue mb-2">Foldable</p>
 <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2">AC Plug</p>
 <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Foldable prongs collapse flat into the housing for backpack and carry-on safety. US, EU, UK, AU plug variants available for OEM.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 text-center">
 <p class="text-3xl font-black text-brandOrange mb-2">92-96%</p>
 <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2">GaN Efficiency</p>
 <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Gallium Nitride chips run cooler and 30-40% smaller than silicon. Higher conversion efficiency means more power in a pocketable shell.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100 text-center">
 <p class="text-3xl font-black text-brandBlue mb-2">1 = 2</p>
 <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 mb-2">Replaces Two Devices</p>
 <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">No separate wall charger, no spare cable. One SKU on the shelf delivers both functions, reducing packaging and cart-add friction.</p>
 </div>
 </div>
 </div>
</section>

